org.apache.juneau.jsonschema.annotation

Class SchemaAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.jsonschema.annotation.SchemaAnnotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotation, Schema

    public class SchemaAnnotation
extends Object
implements Schema
    A concrete implementation of the Schema annotation.

    Annotations can be applied programmatically using BeanContextBuilder.annotations(Annotation...).
